'''魯恩-卡尼夫-高法伯基金'''(Ruane, Cunniff & Goldfarb)是一家由威廉‧Ｊ‧魯恩及李察‧Ｔ‧卡尼夫於1969年在紐約市成立的投資公司。該公司自1970年啟動的旗艦紅杉基金（英文縮寫：SEQUX）在華爾街眾多基金之中有著長期業績最好的紀錄；其並於2013年不再接受新投資者的資金<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748704198004575311042771457112/|title=Sequoia Fund Sticks to What Works|publisher=Wall Street Journal|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120040134/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748704198004575311042771457112|dead-url=no}}.</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.seattletimes.com/business/legendary-sequoia-fund-opens-its-doors-to-new-investors/|title=Legendary Sequoia Fund opens its doors to new investors|publisher=Seattle Times|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2018-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180821094241/https://www.seattletimes.com/business/legendary-sequoia-fund-opens-its-doors-to-new-investors/|dead-url=no}}.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://online.barrons.com/articles/SB50001424052748704330804577139150561809464|title=Sequoia Grows to the Sky|publisher=Barron's|date=2015-05-31|access-date=2016-02-13|archive-date=2015-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713002459/http://online.barrons.com/articles/SB50001424052748704330804577139150561809464|dead-url=no}}.</ref>。魯恩-卡尼夫-高法伯基金管理包括紅杉基金、對沖基金的合夥及私人帳在內的約三百億美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://investment-advisors.credio.com/l/33295/Ruane-Cunniff-And-Goldfarb-Inc|title=Ruane, Cunniff, and Goldfarb|publisher=Credio|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2015-05-13}}{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}.</ref>。現任主席為羅拔‧Ｄ‧高法伯，總裁為大衛‧波普。

== 紅杉基金 ==
魯恩-卡尼夫-高法伯基金最為人所著名的是作為紅杉基金的顧問及發行。紅杉基金的起源可追溯至比爾·魯恩晚年與[[沃伦·巴菲特|禾倫·巴菲特]]的終生友誼。比爾·魯恩於1950年在[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞大學]]一個由[[班傑明·格雷厄姆|班傑明·格雷厄姆]]主持的[[價值投資|價值投資]]講座上初次與[[沃伦·巴菲特|禾倫·巴菲特]]見面。當[[沃伦·巴菲特|禾倫·巴菲特]]於1960年關閉其投資合夥企業時，便建議其客戶連同魯恩投資紅杉基金。1970年，威廉‧Ｊ‧魯恩及李察‧Ｔ‧卡尼夫創立紅杉基金以承接巴菲特的前客戶<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-12-29/cutting-buffett-helps-sequoia-fund-top-value-investor-rankings|title=Cutting Buffett Helps Sequoia Fund Top Value Investor Rankings|publisher=Bloomberg Business|date=2015-05-31|access-date=2016-02-13|archive-date=2016-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413211703/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-12-29/cutting-buffett-helps-sequoia-fund-top-value-investor-rankings|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.barrons.com/focusonfunds/2011/12/30/sequoia-funds-deep-ties-to-warren-buffett-still-paying-off/|title=Sequoia Fund’s Deep Ties To Warren Buffett Still Paying Off|publisher=Barron's|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060903/http://blogs.barrons.com/focusonfunds/2011/12/30/sequoia-funds-deep-ties-to-warren-buffett-still-paying-off/|dead-url=no}}.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/bw/magazine/for-sequoia-life-after-warren-buffett-is-sweet-01052012.html|title=For Sequoia, Life After Warren Buffett Is Sweet|publisher=Bloomberg Business|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308035145/http://www.bloomberg.com/bw/magazine/for-sequoia-life-after-warren-buffett-is-sweet-01052012.html|dead-url=no}}.</ref>。羅拔‧高法伯於其後一年加入。

巴菲特1984年於其論著＜格雷厄姆－多德都市裏的超級投資者＞中寫道：「當我結束我的合夥企業時，我問比爾·魯恩會否成立一個基金以承接我們所有的合夥人，結果他就成立了紅杉基金……比爾是我唯一會向合夥人推薦的人。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www8.gsb.columbia.edu/rtfiles/cbs/hermes/Buffett1984.pdf|title=The Superinvestors of Graham-and-Doddsville|publisher=Columbia Business School|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924030644/http://www8.gsb.columbia.edu/rtfiles/cbs/hermes/Buffett1984.pdf|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}.</ref>他在尋找人選以繼承他於[[波克夏·哈薩威公司|巴郡·哈薩威]]首席投資官的位置時也曾說到：「我在找另一個比爾·魯恩。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/SB117769304545985007|title=Want to Be Next Warren Buffett? The Line Forms in Nebraska|publisher=Wall Street Journal|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506042351/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB117769304545985007|dead-url=no}}.</ref> 

在公司成立的1970年至2015年這45年間，相較於[[标准普尔500指数|標準普爾500]]的10.93%的年化收益，紅杉基金的年化收益率為14.65%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sequoiafund.com/fp-investment-return-table.htm|title=Sequoia Fund Inc. Investment Return Table|publisher=sequoiafund.com|date=2013-09-30|accessdate=2013-10-28|archive-date=2017-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907025637/http://www.sequoiafund.com/fp-investment-return-table.htm|dead-url=no}}.</ref>。據[[晨星公司|晨星公司]]所指，紅杉基金自1970年啟動以來333個滾動10年期當中，332次表現一直優於其他同類大型均衡型基金<ref name="#1"/>。紅杉基金曾於1982年停止接受新投資，26年後於2008年重新接受<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marketwatch.com/story/storied-sequoia-fund-to-reopen-but-has-the-glory-gone|title=Storied Sequoia Fund to reopen, but has the glory gone?|access-date=2016-02-13|archive-date=2018-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180821191906/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/storied-sequoia-fund-to-reopen-but-has-the-glory-gone|dead-url=no}}.</ref>。2010年，晨星公司譽羅拔‧高法伯及大衛‧波普為年度本地股票基金經理以表揚他們於紅杉基金長期的優秀表現<ref>{{cite web|url=http://corporate.morningstar.com/no/asp/subject.aspx?xmlfile=1638.xml&filter=PR4611|title=2010 Morningstar Press release|access-date=2016-02-13|archive-date=2015-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525101059/http://corporate.morningstar.com/no/asp/subject.aspx?xmlfile=1638.xml&filter=PR4611|dead-url=no}}.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2011/01/05/us-morningstar-idUKTRE7044BZ20110105|title=Morningstar names top fund managers for 2010|access-date=2016-02-13|archive-date=2015-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525223228/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2011/01/05/us-morningstar-idUKTRE7044BZ20110105|dead-url=yes}}.</ref>。在2013年，紅杉基金再度停止接受新投資者資金<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sequoiafund.com/images/sequoia%202%20Dec%20%2013.pdf|title=Sequoia Fund Letter to Shareholders|access-date=2016-02-13|archive-date=2014-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101040205/http://www.sequoiafund.com/images/sequoia%202%20Dec%20%2013.pdf|dead-url=yes}}.</ref>。

